para_trans: Bodinala Medium Project Ta. Chandur Bazar, Dist. Amravati. - Regarding grant of first revised administrative sanction.
Government Corrigendum No: Suprama - 2019/82 (Q. No. 29/19) / MP

The Bordeaux Medium Project. Chandur Bazar, Dist. Amravati. Project Reference No. The first revised administrative approval was granted under section 01, subject to certain conditions. In these Terms and Conditions, Clause No. 5.7 The following corrections are being made with respect to the deterioration:
Reference Government Decision No. Condition No. 1 of 01. 5.7-

"Urgent action should be taken to obtain the approval of the Maharashtra Water Resources Regulatory Authority as mentioned by the Secretary level sub-committee, as well as the approval of the Central Water Commission. "

"Does the said project require approval of the Central Water Commission or how? Feedback from the Central Water Commission should be sought in this regard and appropriate action should be taken accordingly. "
This Government Decision Corrigendum is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
